msgid "Create an isolated Python environment and install the Alpha release:"
msgstr "创建隔离的 Python 环境并安装 Alpha 版本："

msgid "Kafka, Iceberg, RocketMQ, Redis, RocksDB, and Serve are optional integrations. Install only the extra required by the application, for example `ray-klein[kafka]`, `ray-klein[iceberg]`, `ray-klein[rocketmq]`, `ray-klein[redis]`, `ray-klein[rocksdb]`, or `ray-klein[serve]`. Use `ray-klein[all]` for an integration development environment. RocketMQ also requires the native `librocketmq` runtime on every worker."
msgstr "Kafka、Iceberg、RocketMQ、Redis、RocksDB 和 Serve 均为可选集成。请只安装应用所需的额外依赖，例如 `ray-klein[kafka]`、`ray-klein[iceberg]`、`ray-klein[rocketmq]`、`ray-klein[redis]`、`ray-klein[rocksdb]` 或 `ray-klein[serve]`。集成开发环境可使用 `ray-klein[all]`。RocketMQ 还要求每个 Worker 都具备原生 `librocketmq` 运行时。"
